cs.SI, cs.CR, cs.CY, cs.SD, cs.DB 

Reasoning: 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is the most likely category as the paper deals with privacy and information leakage in online social networks. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is also likely as the paper discusses the effectiveness of current privacy controls and proposes a system to uncover private information. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is another possible category as the paper touches upon the societal implications of information leakage in online social networks. 
- cs.SD (Software Development and Programming) could be a relevant category as the paper describes the development of a system to uncover private information. 
- cs.DB (Databases) is also a possible category as the paper deals with the retrieval and analysis of data from online social networks.
